vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to 1412 Main Street, LLC, for the use of approximately 441 square feet of land to occupy, maintain, and utilize seven planters and three tree grates on a portion of Main Street right-of-way located near its intersection with Akard Street - Revenue: General Fund $200.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
